title: Pattydoo - Phone pouch / clutch
description:
Please purchase the pattern if you are able to here: https://www.pattydoo.de/en/patterns/phone-pouch-clutch-bowie

If sometime down the line, you have some spare change, go back and pay for it. Support the people and things you enjoy c:

Otherwise, here is the pattern. I know a lot of people don't necessarily have the money to get the pattern, even if it's cheap. Or they can't/don't buy things online. There are various reasons why you can't or won't buy it. Maybe you just like free things, and why not? Whatever, I'm not judging. I'm just making it available
